**Credit Card Fraud Detection Model** on the European Credit Card Fraud Dataset using baseline model (Logistic regression) , Random Forest and XG Boost
Dataset : https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/mlg-ulb/creditcardfraud
Tech-Stack : Python 
**Project Achievement Section**
- Test Accuracy: 99.95%
- Fraud Precision: 91%
- Fraud Recall: 81%
- Fraud F1-Score: 0.85
- Macro F1-Score: 0.93